    Kitsch Eco-Friendly Marble Claw Clip

    4.9(26)
    Kitsch Eco-Friendly Marble Claw Clip adds style and sophistication to your hair with a beautiful marble pattern and glossy finish. Whether you are styling a full or partial updo, the recycled marble acrylic allows you to look your best while being kind on the environment.

    Super pretty and durable

    I purchased the clip in Blonde. It's a very pretty pearlescent cream color -- and not just for those with blonde hair! It feels sturdy and I like that the teeth are a bit flexible, not brittle like some other claw clips. I have very fine hair but a lot of it, and I was worried at first that ...

    I purchased the clip in Blonde. It's a very pretty pearlescent cream color -- and not just for those with blonde hair! It feels sturdy and I like that the teeth are a bit flexible, not brittle like some other claw clips. I have very fine hair but a lot of it, and I was worried at first that the clip wouldn't hold it all since it has a pretty slim profile. It turned out to be the perfect size! Really happy with this purchase and would definitely buy in other colors.
